title: Spring 2016 DH FLEXAIR Intro Featuring Steve Smith, Mark Wallace and Connor Fearon
description:
This trip to Hawaii turned into a great edit from our downhill athletes Steve Smith, Mark Wallace and Connor Fearon. The guys had a great time riding downhill and having fun jumping off of waterfalls, and fishing while shooting our 2016 downhill FLEXAIR intro video.

Music:
"Cloak of the Feathers"
The Sword
